The error is in the second part of the `calc` block:
`_ ‚Č§ ‚ąę ŌČ, ‚ÄĖ‚ąĎ i ‚ąą A, X' i ŌČ‚ÄĖ ^ (2 * m) ‚ąāőľ.prod őľ := by sorry`
