    -- Expand out the power of the sum into a sum over families of indices
    -- `i‚āĀ, ..., i‚āô, j‚āĀ, ..., j‚āô` of `‚ąŹ k, ‚ü®X i‚āĖ, X j‚āĖ‚ü©`. Push the integral inside the sum.
