      rintro ŌČ
      dsimp
      gcongr with k
      exact abs_real_inner_le_norm ..
    -- Rewrite the sum of `ūĚĒľ ‚ąŹ k, ‚ÄĖX i‚āĖ ŌČ‚ÄĖ * ‚ÄĖX j‚āĖ ŌČ‚ÄĖ` over even families of indices
